# Keep the build context lean. The image builds the SPA (frontend stage) and
# cross-compiles the binary (builder stage) from source; it needs go source +
# web/ source, nothing else. go-librespot comes from the base image, so the
# prebuilt respot/ binaries are not part of the Docker build.
.git
.gitlab-ci.yml
bin/
docs/
data/
testdata/
scripts/
respot/                 # go-librespot ships in the base image, not here
ensemble                # prebuilt host binary at repo root
web/node_modules/
web/dist/               # rebuilt in the frontend stage
**/*_test.go
*.md
